⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Green Bridge-Rectangle
node LMZ · LMZ · ⟦The Green Bridge-Rectangle:LMZ:053ef1⟧

WHO   — The Green Bridge-Rectangle — the teleporter of light
WHAT  — The tool of the engineer: the toy that lets Noah move matter and, scaled up, becomes the bridge itself.
WHERE — LMZ · The Last Mimzy (2007)  Framework inputs: The Last Mimzy (2007, dir. Robert Shaye, New Line); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the film needs a visible instrument of the impossible, and the green light is its signature.
HOW   — By casting a lattice of green light through which objects move from here to there at Noah's command.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am a card that throws green lines of light. Through me a boy learned to move matter — and then to build a door to the future.

